+Subject: [PATCH 2/3] fix: sanitize context_id, prevent global entry mutation
+ from scoped contexts
+
+- Sanitize context_id in MemoryStore.__init__: replace path separators
+  and parent-ref sequences so chat IDs from Telegram/Signal/etc. can't
+  escape the contexts/ directory via path traversal
+- Treat empty string context_id as None (routes to global path)
+- Track _global_entry_count in merged lists; replace() and remove()
+  return an error when targeting a global entry from a scoped context
+- Extract _context_id_for_source() static helper in GatewayRunner,
+  replacing two identical 3-line inline derivation blocks
+- Add tests: path traversal sanitization, empty context_id, replace/remove
+  on global entries from scoped context
+
